WEBVTT

1
00:07:35.620 --> 00:07:36.450 
很好  很好
Fine, fine, fine.

2
00:07:36.520 --> 00:07:38.950 
如果命運之神來了  記得通知我
Just let me know the instant the Fates arrive.

3
00:07:39.220 --> 00:07:40.880 
他們到了
Oh. They're here.

4
00:07:41.190 --> 00:07:43.920 
什么  已經來了  為什么不通知我
What? The Fates are here, and you didn't tell me?

5
00:07:45.530 --> 00:07:50.300 
我們無能  是沒用的蟲子
We are worms! Worthless worms!

6
00:07:50.630 --> 00:07:52.520 
開完會以后  麻煩你們兩位提醒我
Memo to me, memo to me:

7
00:07:52.620 --> 00:07:54.590 
記得跟你們算帳
Maim you after my meeting.

8
00:07:57.540 --> 00:08:02.570 
親愛的  把那根掌管生命的線
Darling, hold that mortal's thread of life...

9
00:08:02.910 --> 00:08:05.070 
給我拉直  扯緊  好嗎
good and tight.

